OL,6,FA review has found the PSNI showed
OL,7,F"considerable restraint" in their use
OL,8,Fof baton rounds during recent rioting
OL,9,Fin Northern Ireland.
OL,11,FChief executive of the Police
OL,12,FOmbudsman's Office Hugh Hume said the
OL,13,FPSNI used Attenuating Energy
OL,14,FProjectiles (AEPs) 32 times on five
OL,15,Fdates to help control disorder.
OL,17,FViolence erupted in Ballymena in June
OL,18,Fafter the alleged sexual assault of a
OL,19,Fgirl in the town.
